{"id": "35685", "revid": "49135869", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=35685", "title": "Shadowstep", "text": "The character steps into the Shadow Plane and may move for 7 seconds while others are frozen in time. The caster cannot attack or cast spells while in the Shadow Plane. This counts as a &lt;a href=\"Power%20level\"&gt;level 0&lt;/a&gt; ability. Only &lt;a href=\"Shadowdancers\"&gt;Shadowdancers&lt;/a&gt; can use it.\nUsing this ability counts as a spell with a short casting time, thus it can be interrupted if taking damage while casting.\nThe character can still loot items or open chests while in Shadow Plane. Traps will trigger but the effect will only take place after the duration ends.\nThere is also a &lt;a href=\"Rod%20of%20Shadowstep\"&gt;Rod of Shadowstep&lt;/a&gt; available."}
