{"id": "7462", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7462", "title": "Shyressa", "text": "Shyressa is a &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20%28Elder%29\"&gt;Vampire (Elder)&lt;/a&gt; and a member of the &lt;a href=\"Twisted%20Rune\"&gt;Twisted Rune&lt;/a&gt;. When &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; and party accidently enter the &lt;a href=\"Twisted%20Rune%20Hideout\"&gt;Twisted Rune Hideout&lt;/a&gt;, they will be greeted by the lich &lt;a href=\"Shangalar\"&gt;Shangalar&lt;/a&gt;. After a brief conversation, he will call forth Shyressa and other members of the organization to dispose of \"you\" - the intruders.\nAlthough she is configured to be an Elder Vampire by Hit points and Experience level, she actually has the standard vampire regeneration rate, and level drain attack. Perhaps a developer oversight. \nShe can still use the &lt;a href=\"Domination%20%28Innate%29\"&gt;Vampire Domination&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20Fear\"&gt;Vampire Fear&lt;/a&gt; innate abilities.\nMod content.\nInstallation of &lt;a href=\"Sword%20Coast%20Stratagems\"&gt;Sword Coast Stratagems&lt;/a&gt; mod revises Shyressa. She is now a &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20%28Ancient%29\"&gt;Vampire (Ancient)&lt;/a&gt;, and a level 13/13 &lt;a href=\"Fighter%20/%20Thief\"&gt;Fighter / Thief&lt;/a&gt; with 167 Hit Points and improved &lt;a href=\"THAC0\"&gt;THAC0&lt;/a&gt; and one extra &lt;a href=\"Attacks%20per%20round\"&gt;Attacks per round&lt;/a&gt; raising her melee to 3. Her Dexterity and Intelligence are raised to 20 and 19 respectively. Her &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Class\"&gt;Armor Class&lt;/a&gt; is improved, at least +3 enchanted weapons are required to hit her, and she regenerates 1 HP per second.\nHave a look at the &lt;a href=\"Vampire\"&gt;Vampire&lt;/a&gt; page and the \"Mod content\" section for an overview of what abilities are available through an SCS installation with the \"Improved Vampire\" component.\nShyressa has three innate abilities, including &lt;a href=\"Domination%20%28Innate%29\"&gt;Vampire Domination&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Vampire%20Fear\"&gt;Vampire Fear&lt;/a&gt;, the SCS only \"Mesmerize\" ability which might induce a &lt;a href=\"Feeblemind\"&gt;Feeblemind&lt;/a&gt; effect.\nShe can shape change into a Bat or a Wolf form at will, and back into normal form as required.\nShe can summon \"Children of the Night\" creatures such as Bats, Rats and Wolves, and create a \"Cloud of Bats\" which behaves similarly to a &lt;a href=\"Summon%20Insects\"&gt;Summon Insects&lt;/a&gt; spell.\nShe is \"armed\" with two different melee attack weapons. If the target is protected from &lt;a href=\"Level%20drain\"&gt;Level drain&lt;/a&gt;, she can instead use a \"Blood drain\" attack that reduces &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; instead."}
