{"id": "7919", "revid": "280583", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7919", "title": "Sling of Seeking", "text": "The Sling of Seeking is an enchanted in \"Baldur's Gate II\".\nIn the original game, the reason for the popularity of the Sling of Seeking lay in its ability to use the damage bonus from a wielder's high &lt;a href=\"Strength%23Scores%20table\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; score. In the Enhanced Edition, this is a feature shared by all slings, which is why this Sling's nature and description were changed."}
