enses of the Cat&lt;/a&gt;, the &lt;a href=\"Topsider%27s%20Crutch\"&gt;Topsider's Crutch&lt;/a&gt;, and \u2013 in the \"Enhanced Edition\" \u2013 the spell scroll, Nimbul drops the following &lt;a href=\"Note%20from%20Tazok%20to%20Nimbul\"&gt;letter&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Tazok\"&gt;Tazok&lt;/a&gt;:"}
