{"id": "53144", "revid": "26028522", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=53144", "title": "Noble (BG3)", "text": "Noble is a character &lt;a href=\"Backgrounds%20%28BG3%29\"&gt;background&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20III\"&gt;Baldur's Gate III&lt;/a&gt;\". It conveys a +3 &lt;a href=\"Skill%20Proficiency%20%28BG3%29\"&gt;Skill Proficiency&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"History%20%28BG3%29\"&gt;History&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Persuasion%20%28BG3%29\"&gt;Persuasion&lt;/a&gt;."}
