{"id": "30148", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=30148", "title": "Normal Book", "text": "The Normal Book can be found just inside the front door of &lt;a href=\"Candlekeep%20Library\"&gt;Candlekeep Library&lt;/a&gt; during &lt;a href=\"Chapter%20Six\"&gt;Chapter Six&lt;/a&gt;. The book is entirely blank. It can be theorized that it was either a generic book for testing placed there by accident, or else a remnant of cut content, but its true purpose is not known. In spite of its high probability of being an error, it remains in the .\nDescription.\nNone."}
