{"id": "4882", "revid": "31124876", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4882", "title": "Northwest Baldur's Gate", "text": "Northwest Baldur's Gate is one of nine districts of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate city&lt;/a&gt;. This part of Baldur's Gate is a rich part of the city, judging the clothing of people here and the absence of beggars.\nBuildings.\n&lt;a href=\"Entar%20Silvershield%27s%20Estate\"&gt;Entar Silvershield's Estate&lt;/a&gt;, in the northwest corner, the house of one of the four Grand Dukes in Baldur's Gate. Although there are some valuable items to find, there no special items. Also, if &lt;a href=\"Eldoth\"&gt;Eldoth&lt;/a&gt; is in your party, your party is able to recruit &lt;a href=\"Skie%20Silvershield\"&gt;Skie Silvershield&lt;/a&gt;, a companion and the daughter of the Grand Duke.\n&lt;a href=\"Helm%20and%20Cloak\"&gt;Helm and Cloak&lt;/a&gt; Inn, southeast part of the area, is a luxurious inn. The Merry Fools can be found here and after talking to them, another group of adventurers walk in, who are a bit rough. One member of the group drops &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Axe%20of%20Mauletar\"&gt;Battle Axe of Mauletar&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Degrodel%27s%20Home\"&gt;Degrodel's Home&lt;/a&gt;, which is guarded by hostile creatures, greet you when entering his house. If you talk to &lt;a href=\"Degrodel\"&gt;Degrodel&lt;/a&gt;, after slaying them, the party can start the &lt;a href=\"Searching%20for%20Balduran%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;Searching for Balduran's Helmet&lt;/a&gt; side quest.\n&lt;a href=\"Laerta%20and%20Louise%27s%20Home\"&gt;Laerta and Louise's Home&lt;/a&gt; is inhabitated by twins &lt;a href=\"Laerta%20and%20Louise\"&gt;Laerta and Louise&lt;/a&gt;, there you can start another side quest which may give you the &lt;a href=\"Wand%20of%20Polymorphing\"&gt;Wand of Polymorphing&lt;/a&gt; as a reward.\n&lt;a href=\"Quinn%27s%20Home\"&gt;Quinn's Home&lt;/a&gt; is the start of &lt;a href=\"Quinn%27s%20Friend\"&gt;Quinn's Friend&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"side%20quest\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt;.\n&lt;a href=\"Pheirkas%27s%20Home\"&gt;Pheirkas's Home&lt;/a&gt; is the home of the dwarf &lt;a href=\"Pheirkas\"&gt;Pheirkas&lt;/a&gt;.\nAn &lt;a href=\"Generic%20Tavern%20and%20Inn%20%28Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23Tavern_and_Inn_.28AR0165.2FAR0166.29\"&gt;unnamed inn&lt;/a&gt; north of the Helm and Cloak.\nSeveral &lt;a href=\"Generic%20homes%20%28northwest%20Baldur%27s%20Gate%29\"&gt;generic homes&lt;/a&gt; with very minor loot.\nNortheast corner.\nThe map has a walled-off section at the northeast corner. This part can be accessed from the &lt;a href=\"North%20Baldur%27s%20Gate%23Black%20Dragon%20Gate\"&gt;Black Dragon Gate&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"North%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;North Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt;.\nReputation Trap.\nIf your Reputation is lower than 3 you will be attacked by a group of three &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Enforcer%20%28Baldur%27s%20Gate%29%23FLAMPUN\"&gt;Flaming Fist Enforcer&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Scout\"&gt;Flaming Fist Scout&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Flaming%20Fist%20Battle%20Wizard\"&gt;Flaming Fist Battle Wizard&lt;/a&gt;. This group of soldiers will attack suddenly both on the streets and in &lt;a href=\"Entar%20Silvershield%27s%20Estate\"&gt;Entar Silvershield's Estate&lt;/a&gt;.\nNearby areas.\nCity map overview.\n City grid you are at the X:\n X|o|o NW|&lt;a href=\"North%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"Northeast%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;NE&lt;/a&gt; \n o|o|o &lt;a href=\"West%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"Central%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"East%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;E&lt;/a&gt; \n o|o|o &lt;a href=\"Southwest%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;SW&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"South%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;|&lt;a href=\"Southeast%20Baldur%27s%20Gate\"&gt;SE&lt;/a&gt;"}
