{"id": "12028", "revid": "44830706", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12028", "title": "Abdel Adrian", "text": "Abdel Adrian is a male &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"fighter\"&gt;fighter&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Bhaalspawn\"&gt;Bhaalspawn&lt;/a&gt; and the version of &lt;a href=\"Gorion%27s%20Ward\"&gt;Gorion's Ward&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Realms\"&gt;Forgotten Realms&lt;/a&gt; novels.\nInformation about Abdel's &lt;a href=\"alignment\"&gt;alignment&lt;/a&gt; varies, depending on source: in the original games and in the ' he is &lt;a href=\"neutral%20good\"&gt;neutral good&lt;/a&gt;, while the &lt;a href=\"Character%20Generation\"&gt;pregenerated character&lt;/a&gt; from the ' and \"\" is &lt;a href=\"chaotic%20good\"&gt;chaotic good&lt;/a&gt;. The &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28novels%29\"&gt;\"Baldur's Gate\" novels&lt;/a&gt; state he was &lt;a href=\"chaotic%20neutral\"&gt;chaotic neutral&lt;/a&gt; and has become &lt;a href=\"true%20neutral\"&gt;true neutral&lt;/a&gt; in later events (&lt;a href=\"w%3Ac%3Aforgottenrealms%3ADungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons\"&gt;\"Dungeons &amp; Dragons\" 5th edition&lt;/a&gt;).\nIn-game.\nAbdel Adrian is one of the protagonists in the pre-generated save game that came with . He is also one of the pregenerated player characters in the .\nForgotten Realms.\nAbdel is the protagonist of the &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28novels%29\"&gt;\"Baldur's Gate\" novels&lt;/a&gt;. In the novels, he is described as being 7 feet/ 2.13m tall, having long, ink-black hair and dark eyes, unlike his in-game portrait. He was born in 1343 DR, which would make him 25 years old at the beginning of the games.\nHe grew to become over a century old and became one of the Grand Dukes of &lt;a href=\"Baldur%27s%20Gate%20%28city%29\"&gt;Baldur's Gate&lt;/a&gt; in his later years. He died at the age of 136."}
