{"id": "47863", "revid": "47673695", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=47863", "title": "Achon", "text": "Achon is a &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Thieves\"&gt;Shadow Thief&lt;/a&gt; and former trusted chief assistant of &lt;a href=\"Aran%20Linvail\"&gt;Aran Linvail&lt;/a&gt; who tried to assassinate Linvail in the name of guild loyalty. He is now awaiting his gruesome fate in the prison room within the secret &lt;a href=\"Aran%20Linvail%27s%20Hideout\"&gt;hideout&lt;/a&gt; that's located beneath the &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Thief%20Guildhall\"&gt;Shadow Thief Guildhall&lt;/a&gt;. Conversation with the elf reveals that Aran may not be someone who's promises can be trusted.\nDialogue.\n\"Hmph. I suppose that you must be one of Aran's new favorites. You don't have the look of one who's worked &lt;HISHER&gt; way up through the ranks of the guild.\"\n\"I am Achon... I was once Aran's lieutenant, his chief assistant and right-hand man. I was loyal to the guild above all, and that was my greatest fault. I thought I was doing the guild a favor by trying to assassinate Aran.\"\n\"Perhaps I was right, perhaps I was wrong. Perhaps Aran will not destroy our guild. Perhaps the other guild run by that... that woman... will be eliminated. I suppose I shall never know.\"\n\"The only thing I am certain of now is that my punishment shall be more agonizing and prolonged than anything you can dream of.\"\n\"Now leave me be, newcomer. There is nothing you can do for me or to me, and I have nothing left but to await my fate at Aran's whim.\""}
{"id": "15596", "revid": "27884103", "url": "https://baldursgate.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15596", "title": "Acid", "text": "Acid is a status effect which inflicts acid damage on the affected character until the duration of the effects wears or if the character dies from its effects. The amount of damage and duration depends on the means by which it is inflicted. This status effect can be inflicted by the spell &lt;a href=\"Melf%27s%20Acid%20Arrow\"&gt;Melf's Acid Arrow&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe means to prevent any character from this effect are acid and magic resistance and the spell &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Immunity\"&gt;Spell Immunity&lt;/a&gt;. The items which can prevent this are &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Magic%20Blocking\"&gt;Potion of Magic Blocking&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Protection%20From%20Acid%20%28protection%20scroll%29\"&gt;Protection From Acid scroll&lt;/a&gt;.\nOnce affected, one can only remove the further acid damage in the coming rounds by using a &lt;a href=\"Potion%20of%20Magic%20Blocking\"&gt;Potion of Magic Blocking&lt;/a&gt; or casting &lt;a href=\"Dispel%20Magic\"&gt;Dispel Magic&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Protection%20From%20Magic\"&gt;Protection From Magic&lt;/a&gt;."}
